      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you've reached a place of profound exhaustion where the idea of fighting feels more painful than the stillness. That sense of surrender can feel like peace, but it's also a very dangerous place to settle into. Even if the external things feel irreparable, your own life still holds value, and there are ways to find release that don't involve giving up. Please, before you let the darkness win, reach out to someone who can listen without judgment, like calling 988.",
